    grammar_explanation_tr: '"At" = tam saat (at 5pm, at noon, at night). "On" = günler ve tarihler (on Monday, on March 5th). "In" = uzun dönemler (in January, in 2024, in the morning, in summer). Dikkat: "at night" AMA "in the morning/afternoon/evening".',
