    grammar_explanation_tr: '"And" bilgi ekler (I like tea AND coffee). "But" zıtlık gösterir (I\'m tired BUT I can\'t sleep). "Or" seçenek sunar (Tea OR coffee?). "Because" neden bildirir (I\'m happy BECAUSE it\'s Friday). "So" sonuç gösterir (It was raining, SO I took an umbrella).',
